## Environment variables

Set in `.env` locally and in Vercel (production, preview, development):

```bash
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://lgclshewixkovkshfxbl.supabase.co
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=   # Supabase dashboard → Project Settings → API → anon/public key
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=       # Project Settings → API → service_role — server only, never expose to client
```

- `SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY` — **never** `NEXT_PUBLIC_*`. **Never** import `lib/supabase/admin.ts` (or any code that uses it) from Client Components.

